column5: Sorry goofed - work in progress - see above  Don
Thanks for the Sunday read Don. Glad to see another that can have a great day on the water fishless !
Thanks Wayne - If I let no fish ruin a great day of fishing - I might as well take up Golf!!   Don
Ok now I really goofed - deleted both reports by mistake - any way to get back - or gone for good and start typing?   Don

Hey don dont feel too bad !!! my buds were there all day yesterday...they said lots of boats,bright sun & warm temps...and yes like you said...NO FISH CAUGHT !!!!   they never even had a rod go off.they didnt see any other boats catch any either...all the people they talked to said the same no fish....they are there it just wasnt the day that the walleyes wanted to come out and play..  ..oh well keep trying,im heading there real soon too,and i hope it picks up by then...i cant wait for our OFC G2G WEEKEND !!!!!   thanks for the fun report oh ya they said they got SUNBURNED AS WELL,IN NOVEMBER..LOL..LOL..LOL
